conch2.server
Class CommandProcessor

java.lang.Object
  conch2.server.CommandProcessor

public class CommandProcessor
extends java.lang.Object

All helper functions to process each command are grouped in this class. Each time a command is executed, the result will go to the outputDoc w3c document in XML file format.

addCompMeta

public void addCompMeta(java.lang.String name,
                        java.lang.String vendor,
                        java.lang.String category,
                        java.lang.String constString)
This function inserts an entry into the ComponentMeta table. It includes component name, its vendor, the category it belongs to, and the constraints applied to it in plain text. The componentId is left as auto-increment.

Parameters:
name - component name
vendor - component vendor
category - the category it falls in
constString - constraints applied to this component

authenticate

public void authenticate(java.lang.String name,
                         java.lang.String password)
This function checks whether the given username and password is legal according to the Testers table. If yes, it marks a record in the Session table, which includes the time this session starts. Currently, we don't care about the ActiveStatus attribute.

Parameters:
name - username
password - password of the user
